# [Interview #1155: Calamity-Philadelphia, PA, Entry #50](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=1155#50)

#### Question

He asked for the name of an “observed but un-named spren”

#### Brandon Sanderson

There are none, they’ve all been named.
